    <category term="设计模式" scheme="https://leithda.github.io/tags/%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F/"/>
    
  </entry>
  
  <entry>
    <title>享元模式</title>
    <link href="https://leithda.github.io/posts/2031750427.html"/>
    <id>https://leithda.github.io/posts/2031750427.html</id>
    <published>2021-05-27T04:50:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-05-27T07:18:23.397Z</updated>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;blockquote class=&quot;blockquote-center&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;享元模式(Flyweight Pattern)主要用于减少创建对象的数量，以减少内存占用和提高性能。这种类型的设计模式属于结构型模式，它提供了减少对象数量从而改善应用所需的对象结构的方式。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;/blockquote&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
    <category term="理论" scheme="https://leithda.github.io/categories/%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA/"/>
    
    <category term="设计模式" scheme="https://leithda.github.io/categories/%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA/%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F/"/>
    
    
    <category term="设计模式" scheme="https://leithda.github.io/tags/%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F/"/>
    
  </entry>
  
  <entry>
    <title>原型模式</title>
    <link href="https://leithda.github.io/posts/153761970.html"/>
    <id>https://leithda.github.io/posts/153761970.html</id>
    <published>2021-05-27T04:50:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-05-27T07:18:10.792Z</updated>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;blockquote class=&quot;blockquote-center&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;使用原型实例指定要创建对象的类型，通过复制这个原型来创建新对象。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;/blockquote&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
