  <entry>
    <title>责任链模式</title>
    <link href="https://leithda.github.io/posts/1644716670.html"/>
    <id>https://leithda.github.io/posts/1644716670.html</id>
    <published>2021-05-27T04:50:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-05-27T08:54:52.737Z</updated>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;blockquote class=&quot;blockquote-center&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;顾名思义，责任链模式(Chain of Responsibility Pattern) 为请求创建了一个接收者对象的链。这种模式给予请求的类型，对请求的发送者和接收者进行解耦。这种类型的设计模式属于行为型模式。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;/blockquote&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
